---
description: Lingua core engineering rules
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Lingua is accuracy-first.

Never invent language facts.
Never treat transcript/raw content as trusted truth by default.
Only write UserProgress for trusted Vocabulary or Sentence anchors.
Keep changes deterministic, modular, and explainable.
Prefer minimal targeted edits.
When changing backend behavior, keep frontend payload expectations consistent.
Run the relevant build/check commands before finishing.
